type.description:
## Tame

---


[Bi-entity Action Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/bientity_action_types/tame)

Tames the target entity with the actor entity as the owner. Only works on tameable entities such as wolves or cats.

Type ID: `origins:tame`

---

### Examples

```json
"bientity_action": {
    "type": "origins:tame"
}
```
